rating_comment: It was a good stay. We stayed for a short time before airport transfer so couldn't explore much. Dinner provided by the host and family was very tasty we enjoyed it. Thank you.

We were a group of friends. This is a lovely and peaceful homestay near airport. we enjoyed our last day here.
Kushal is a lovely host, she is very helpful.
We loved everything about the place- ambience, comfort, interiors.
Thanks once again.
